desc_short	-----								A VR minigolf experience taking you to a beautifully landscaped course high above the clouds. Single player, online and local multiplayer, and a course editor (coming soon) allow you to build, share, and play other user created holes. No swing or power meters here, simply swing the club to play.							
developer									Futuretown								
